{"tid":1461991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成個社會嘅命脈竟然會靠晒一個咁弱嘅關節","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:49:25.000Z","uid":259321,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7912e7c100bcc16ee29f4dbc8bd798e8724bb8a3","tid":1461991,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"popo 呢度冇你嘅事可以出返去先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尋日一lot 野cancel 半日機<br />\n唔係退錢就塞落下一班機<br />\n暑假呢啲Peak season 班班機都爆<br />\n首先宜家<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">航空公司係冧檔都死唔掂</span></span><br />\n<br />\n經貿乜乜果啲固然<br />\n但從航空公司平日超賣機位<br />\n冇Buffer位 &times; peak season &times; cancel flight<br />\n最先跪低一定係航空公司<br />\n因為對航空公司嚟講計數 (幾時有機，放到幾多客 etc.) 係命脈嚟<br />\n但流水社運個本質就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不能被估計 (Unpredictable)</span></span><br />\n宜家所有電腦計開果啲已經唔適用<br />\n靠人手估估下<br />\n出現無限Plan B plan C<br />\n但對住 unpredictable 嘅be water<br />\n去到Plan &infin; 都係肯撚定搞唔掂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">推論出 be water 本質強大之處：<br />\n不確定性 (unpredictability)</div><ins></ins></span></span><br />\n用嚟<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打擊需要穩定嘅關節</span></span>就係Be water 嘅強項<br />\n<br />\n綜合返香港機場係有幾個<span style=\"color: gold;\">特質</span>令佢被Be water 大剋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><ins></ins>]<br />\n<br />\n但諗返係神奇：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成個社會嘅命脈竟然會靠晒一個咁弱嘅關節</span></span><br />\n亦都係因為機場對社會嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">風險系數大到仆街</span></span><br />\n對be water 嚟講機場只不過係高CP值嘅 low lying fruit.<br />\n<br />\n低成本高效益<br />\n一定要繼續塞機場<br />\n只要果日FC到佢地Cancel flight<br />\n就可以買杯雪糕<br />\n食住雪糕行出東涌返屋企 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8260519e4ffb82135927b766f57c9e6cfcc7af","tid":1461991,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:50:07.000Z","msg":"綜合返香港機場係有幾個<span style=\"color: gold;\">特質</span>令佢被Be water 大剋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><ins></ins>]"},{"pid":"850368fb223dc856fd4b283fdb193cf72b52a71b","tid":1461991,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:50:36.000Z","msg":"綜合返香港機場係有幾個<span style=\"color: gold;\">特質</span>令佢被Be water 大剋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><ins></ins>]"},{"pid":"967899c968ad5b27c73e983f9ba6a2cf36ece9e9","tid":1461991,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:54:57.000Z","msg":"綜合返香港機場係有幾個<span style=\"color: gold;\">特質</span>令佢被Be water 大剋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><ins></ins>]"},{"pid":"b8e255bce8fd6df0205f3b63fef9dece65e00e54","tid":1461991,"uid":167435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:00:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"faac76eeee8bb6d39e881ed32c3bb6f2e693e17c","tid":1461991,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:03:47.000Z","msg":"搞死航空公司對政府可以造成幾大既傷害?"},{"pid":"aea64fe945e6e47ccc803927f861e0b680f99db8","tid":1461991,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:06:17.000Z","msg":"大家要快d開始傾<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大方向</span></strong></span><br />\n3毛5毛開始想<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">重施故技</span></span></strong>用斟酌「阻人上機」個point黎<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化大家</span></span></strong><br />\n但記得大家塞爆機場個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span></strong></span>就係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場從而阻人上機</span></span></strong>以造成<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">巨大經濟損失</span></span></strong><br />\n但最好隔日咁做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>個人認為呢位師兄言之有物<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n[理性討論] 有死線前提搞機場/隔日搞機場比日日搞更好 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"55336135a58f236696da6b138a085151d3eb92d8","tid":1461991,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:10:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e301eb8baf119dd2a20436018f4c87d52e70b47","tid":1461991,"uid":35216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8a953a169d7e7e53de95d0b64f7179cadf4a4bfc","tid":1461991,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:49:25.000Z","msg":"推"}]}